data.description: This adorable Cape Cod style home is ready and waiting for you! In 2020 a new septic was installed, heating system was revamped, new thermostat system and a 40 gallon external water heater! As you enter the home you will see an open living room to dining area and stainless steel topped pennisula in the kitchen. Access to the deck is off the dining area too. This floorplan works for many with a bedroom on the main living level next to the bathroom, an office / lounge space next to the stairs leading to the second floor. Upstairs you will find two generous sized bedrooms each with their own little reading nook. The backyard is huge and a garden is there too! Wonderful open space right off the sizable deck. Sweet little neighborhood to take a stroll. Such a convenient location, seconds on to Rt. 9G! Close to the middle school too! Easy to zip up to Rhinebeck, over to the Culinary or to a hike in one of the many area parks. Jump on it! This is right sized and so cute!
